      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.wFTC0sGqdpnZUib4]{Gear Boost}</p>\n<p>When you hit a creature within 30 feet of you while using a weapon with the bright weapon special property, the radiance partially blinds the target, giving it the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.YjE6UGzwOTfO9p4g]{dazzled} condition for 1 round. If you hit multiple creatures at the same time (such as with an @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.Nrf6oy9pJwcEmryP.JournalEntryPage.nXkFsyxk7Vybdn7G#automatic]{automatic}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.Nrf6oy9pJwcEmryP.JournalEntryPage.nXkFsyxk7Vybdn7G#blast]{blast}, or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.Nrf6oy9pJwcEmryP.JournalEntryPage.nXkFsyxk7Vybdn7G#explode]{explode} weapon), only the creature nearest to you or at the center of the explosion (your choice if multiple creatures are equidistant) is affected.</p>"
